cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.CL

The paper deals with recommendation systems, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of neural networks for collaborative filtering falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of textual descriptions of items, which falls under natural language processing (cs.CL) and the evaluation of the proposed framework involves metrics such as precision and recall, which are commonly used in information retrieval and search (cs.SI).
